The Debut of ShiVerBeck. Come out this Wednesday at the Holy Oak, 7:30-9:30 as Nick Zubeck (of Sun Kil Moon and Barzin fame), Handsome Mark Laver (of Earthtones and Dirt Farmers fame) as well as PPF's Tim Shia debut their brand new album, Starlets, featuring art by Jacob Zubeck. Available only on [bandcamp](https://shiverbeck.bandcamp.com/releases)
